flowchart TD
    A[Payment Request] --> B[Payment Orchestration Layer]

    B --> C{Routing Decision}

    C -->|Card US/EU| D[Primary: Stripe]
    C -->|Card India| E[Primary: Razorpay]
    C -->|UPI India| F[Razorpay UPI]
    C -->|Pix Brazil| G[Primary: EBANX / PagSeguro]
    C -->|OXXO Mexico| H[Primary: Conekta]
    C -->|WeChat/Alipay| I[Primary: Adyen]
    C -->|SEA Wallets| J[Primary: Xendit]
    C -->|Fallback| K[Secondary Provider]

    D --> L{Stripe Healthy?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Process via Stripe]
    L -->|No - Circuit Open| N[Failover to Adyen]

    E --> O{Razorpay Healthy?}
    O -->|Yes| P[Process via Razorpay]
    O -->|No| Q[Failover to Cashfree]

    M --> R{Result}
    N --> R
    P --> R
    Q --> R
    F --> R
    G --> R
    H --> R
    I --> R
    J --> R
    K --> R

    R -->|Success| S[✅ Payment Confirmed]
    R -->|Soft Decline| T[Retry with alternate provider]
    R -->|Hard Decline| U[❌ Payment Failed]

    T --> C

    B --> V[Orchestrator Features]
    V --> W[Token vault - PCI scope reduction]
    V --> X[Smart routing - cost optimization]
    V --> Y[Unified reporting - single dashboard]
    V --> Z[Provider health - circuit breaker]

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style S fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style U fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style T fill:#F5A623,color:#fff
    style B fill:#F5A623,color:#fff
